  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Craft or refine Aronium from <span class=\"name name-earth\">Paraffinium</span> and <span class=\"name name-earth\">Ionized Cobalt</span>. Refining advanced products requires a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Large Refiner</span>.<br>Paraffinium is found in large deposits on <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">lush planets</span> with an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Analysis Visor</span>.<br>Refine Chlorine from <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Salt</span>, which is harvested from <span class=\"name name-technology\">underwater mineral deposits</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "可利用阿洛姆石蜡<span class=\"name name-earth\">和</span>离子钴<span class=\"name name-earth\">制作或精炼</span>。精炼先进的产品需要<span class=\"name name-technology\">大型精炼机</span>。<br>石蜡能在<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">茂盛星球</span>上使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>在大型矿床中找到。<br>从<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">盐</span>中能精炼出氯，盐可从<span class=\"name name-technology\">水下矿藏</span>中采集到。",
    "TencentChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-earth\">矿脂</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">氯</span>制作或精炼出阿洛姆。精炼先进的产品需要<span class=\"name name-technology\">大型精炼机</span>。<br>矿脂能在<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">茂盛星球</span>上使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>在大型矿床中找到。<br>从<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">盐</span>中精炼出氯，盐能从<span class=\"name name-technology\">水下矿藏</span>中采集到。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "將<span class=\"name name-earth\">鑞</span>及<span class=\"name name-earth\">離子化鈷</span>製作或精製成鑨。精製先進產品需使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">大型精製機</span>。<br>鑞可用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析護目鏡</span>在<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">蒼翠星球</span>的大型資源產地找到。<br>將<span class=\"name name-technology\">水底礦資源產地</span>所採收的<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">鹽</span>精製成氯。"
  },
